videos.description: Montez Mathis sends a nice no-look bounce pass to Shaquille Doorson to brings it home with a huge dunk.
videos.headline: Mathis sends no-look pass to Doorson for slam

videos.description: Zavier Simpson flings it full court to Jordan Poole who finishes with massive dunk.
videos.headline: Simpson sends full-court pass to Poole for the jam

videos.description: Xavier Simpson blows the commentators away with an impressive running hook shot to increase Michigan's lead 29-12.
videos.headline: Simpson amazes with running hook shot

videos.description: Geo Baker drops long-range three to help his team get some momentum capping off an 8-0 run and the fans love it.
videos.headline: Baker sends crowd into frenzy with step-back three

videos.description: Zavier Simpson whips it over his head to Ignas Brazdeikis who drops the long-range three for Michigan.
videos.headline: Simpson whips it back to Brazdeikis who sinks the three
